Ninja Warrior: UK - Series 4, Episode 6




Semi-Final 2

Competitors from across the nation test their strength, speed and courage in part two of the obstacle-course challenge's semi-final, hosted by Ben Shephard, Rochelle Humes and Chris Kamara. Those who make it to the end of the adrenaline-fuelled mission face one final task - scaling the heights of a tower named Mount Midoriyama - as they battle it out for the title of Ninja Warrior UK.




Original Air Date: 19-May-2018
